<html>
<h2> Entitlement rates and just how much do they vary across the country?</h2>
<br>
<p><b>Listen to this article</b></p>
<hr>
  <p> As expected, due to different standards of living, the median hourly rate of free entitlement given to local authorities varies. <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/early-years-funding-2020-2021">Data released by the government</a> gives a clear picture as to how much regional variation there is.</p>
<div class="flourish-embed flourish-table" data-src="visualisation/6519252"><script src="https://public.flourish.studio/resources/embed.js"></script></div>


